api.body:
require "pixcHelper"
require "pixcProtocolHttp"
require "pixcNetwork"
math.randomseed(os.time())
self.stop = false
if self.pixcHelper ~= nil then
	return 
end
if self.jsonlib == nil then
	self.jsonlib = require "json" 
end


self.network = createPixcNetwork()
self.helper = createPixcHelper(pixc,self())
self.helper.arrayRemove = function (t, fnKeep,extInfo,optPreRm)
    local j, n = 1, #t;

    for i=1,n do
        if (fnKeep(t, i, j,extInfo)) then
            -- Move i's kept value to j's position, if it's not already there.
            if (i ~= j) then
                t[j] = t[i];
                t[i] = nil;
            end
            j = j + 1; -- Increment position of where we'll place the next kept value.
        else
			if(optPreRm ~= nil) then
				optPreRm(t[i])
            	t[i] = nil;
			else
				t[i] = nil;
			end
        end
    end

    return t;
end
self.helper.toBool = function (str, default)
    if type(str) == 'boolean' then 
        return str 
    end
    if( str == "true") then
        return true
    end
    if( str == "false") then
        return false
    end
    return default
end
self.version = self.helper:getProperty("Version","")
pixc.log(self().." Module Version: "..self.version)

self.currentEntrieToDeleteMap = {}
self.protocol = createPixcProtocolHttp()
self.avCall = require("pixcCall")
self.protocol:setStatusCallbacks(
	function (...) pixc.log(...) end)

self.url = self.helper:getProperty("ISAAC URL","")
self.externalId = self.helper:getProperty("Module ID","")

self.reservedAction = {};
self.reservedScheduleEvent = {};
self.Data.loadFromProperty();
self.scheduleName = "Main"..self()
--pixc.log(self().." "..self.scheduleName)

local schedule = Utils.Scheduler.getSchedule(self.scheduleName)
if schedule ~= nil and schedule.getHandleInt() ~= 0 then
	--Schedule does not exist create it.
	schedule.remove()
end
self.schedUpdateInterval = self.helper:getProperty("Scheduler Update Interval","30s")
self.isaacAdapterIP = pixc.getRoot().Utils.Network.convertLocalAdapterEntry(self.helper:getProperty("Network Adapter",""),true,true)
self.heartbeatTriggerActive = false
self.schdedulerTriggerActive = false
self.Helper.triggerHeartbeat()

self.apiKey = "";
self.Schedule.getSchedule()
self.Events.getEvents()
self.Helper.triggerGetCalendarEntries()

--
local currentEntries = self.schedule.getAllEntries();
--pixc.log("nr of Entries",#currentEntries)
local currentEntrieNameToHdl = {}
if self.jsonlib == nil then
	self.jsonlib = require "json" 
end
for k,v in ipairs(currentEntries) do
	local name = v.get("_id")
	if(not self.Schedule.isReservedScheduleEntry(v.get("name"))) then
    	if self.currentEntrieToDeleteMap[name] ~= nil then
			self.currentEntrieToDeleteMap[name] = self.currentEntrieToDeleteMap[name] - 1
		end
		currentEntrieNameToHdl[name] = v
	end	
end
local json = {};
for k , v  in ipairs(self.calendar1) do
	json = {}
	json["name"] = v.displayName
	json["_id"] = v._id
	json["start"] = v.startTime
	json["end"] = v.endTime
	local action = {}
	action[v.itemId..""] = ""
	json["actions"] = action
	local jsonStr = self.jsonlib.encode(json);
	if self.currentEntrieToDeleteMap[v._id] == nil then
-- add
		pixc.log(self().." adding",v.displayName,v._id)
		self.schedule.createEntry(jsonStr)
		self.currentEntrieToDeleteMap[v._id] = 3
	else
-- update
		--pixc.log(self().." updateing",v.displayName,v._id)
		currentEntrieNameToHdl[v._id].update(jsonStr)
		self.currentEntrieToDeleteMap[v._id] = 3
	end
end
local updatedDeletedMap = {}
for k,v in pairs(self.currentEntrieToDeleteMap) do
	if v  < 1 then
		pixc.log(self().." removing",k)	
		currentEntrieNameToHdl[k].remove()
	else
		updatedDeletedMap[k] = v
	end
end
self.currentEntrieToDeleteMap = updatedDeletedMap
updatedDeletedMap = nil
